This recipe has become a favorite. It's really delicious & so easy to prepare. I use a blend of mushrooms, including shitakes, to keep the cost down. I also use white whine instead of red, because that's usually what we have on hand. It improves the appearance of the dish as well. Red wine makes the sauce pink!

