Although this dish was very easy to make and not very labor intensive, the end result was a disappointment. I found the flavors to be too bland (although I added plenty of salt). Also, cooking the mushrooms with the wine until the sauce reduced took forever and in the end the mushrooms were wine-soaked and soggy. I won't be making this recipe again.

