Rating: 3
This dish was done for me this weekend by my sister. I am not a lover of pork, but this dish was so wonderful, that I came here to get the recipe. She served the pork and compote over twice baked mashed potatoes seasoned with gouda and parmesan cheese, garlic, sour cream, milk and butter. Definitely a dinner party recipe, and so easy to fix.